description: Wuhan Fried Bats (WUHAN) is a deflating memecoin based on the Coronavirus and the corona-chan meme. Everytime a person is infected or dies a portion of the max supply will be burned among this there is 2% in-built deflation whenever transactions are sent between people. Portion of the token sales are going into Charity fighting against the virus.
